$interpreted: Yan-Bo: N-no...
Edensnatch Manager: Save... me...
Edensnatch Manager: Y-Yan-Bo...
Yan-Bo: Stay with me, I'm taking you to get help!
Edensnatch Manager: This is all... your fault...
Yan-Bo: What?
Edensnatch Manager: It's your fault everyone's dead...
Edensnatch Manager: You never cared for your fellow Tribespeople, all you cared about was martial arts... Call yourself a Master... You don't... deserve...
Yan-Bo: ...You're in shock!
Yan-Bo: N-no, you're out of energy...
Surprised Hoodlum: Is everything taken care of?
Surprised Hoodlum: If they're all dead then we'd better get back... Who are you!?
Yan-Bo: Who sent you!?
Surprised Hoodlum: Another Capybara... Could this one be Yan-Bo!? Damn, Sennosuke's left already...
Yan-Bo: (Sennosuke... So this is all to do with Kaito's death?)
Yan-Bo: ...Answer me, did Sennosuke order you here?
Surprised Hoodlum: So what! You guys killed Kaito first!
Yan-Bo: I didn't kill Kaito...
Surprised Hoodlum: Liar! That Capybara just said you cheated and got Kaito killed because they were so poor! You're to blame!
Surprised Hoodlum: See! You're speechless! I should have you tied up so that the Boss'll give me a tidy reward!
Yan-Bo: (All I wanted was people's respect, to be called Master...)
Yan-Bo: (I never paid any attention to the dire straits my Tribe was in, I just focussed on that competition...)
Yan-Bo: This sign... means nothing to me...
Yan-Bo: It's all my fault...
: Some days later...
Busy Hoodlum: Sir, we've had no news of Yan-Bo today.
Secret Society Boss: You may go.
Busy Hoodlum: Yes, sir.
Secret Society Boss: The Capybara Tribe has been wiped out. Yan-Bo really knows how to hide himself...
Sennosuke: ...We've still not found him, after so many days of searching. Has he fled the East?
Secret Society Boss: ...No matter where he's escaped to, the Capybaras are extinct now, and Kaito's vengeance is complete.
Sennosuke: Kaito won't have had his vengeance while Yan-Bo still lives! Please, allow me to kill that scumbag with my own hands!
Secret Society Boss: Oh?
Secret Society Boss: It'll take a lot to catch up to Yan-Bo now, and it won't be in our interests neither.
Sennosuke: But you said that you were Master's brother in arms... That you wanted to avenge him...
Secret Society Boss: Feelings are one thing, and interests another. The Capybaras have been decimated. Everything else is superfluous.
Secret Society Boss: But for Kaito's sake... I can see you have what it takes to be part of our Society. How about it?
Secret Society Boss: Join us, and I'll help you find Yan-Bo and deal with him as you like.
Sennosuke: (For Master...!)
Sennosuke: Yes... I want in!
Secret Society Boss: From this day on, you are one of us.
Sennosuke: Thank you, Boss!
Sennosuke: Just wait, Master. Even if it means going against your teachings...
Sennosuke: I'll do all I can to kill Yan-Bo and avenge you.
